        {
            "id": 5969300,
            "title": "《國金頭條》美英達成貿易協議,特朗普號召入市,美股報升",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社9日專訊》美英周四(8日)達成關稅戰以來的首個貿易協議,特朗普同時表示有意下調對中國關稅,並號召「最好大家都去買股票。」美股三大指數報升。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　美國財政部長貝森特將於周六(10日),與中國國務院副總理何立峰在瑞士展開貿易會談,市場對談判感到樂觀。<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道指</a>高開後,一度升逾600點,高見41773點;標指一度升1.58%,納指則曾升2.02%。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道指</a>收市升254.48點,或0.62%,報41368.45點;標普500指數升32.66點,或0.58%,報5663.94點;納指升189.98點,或1.07%,報17928.14點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　周三(7日)大跌逾7%的Alphabet日內升1.9%。<a href=\"https://crypto.cnyes.com/BTC/24h\" target=\"_blank\">比特幣</a>日內升至三個月高位,重上10萬美元大關,推動<a href=\"https://crypto.cnyes.com/BTC/24h\" target=\"_blank\">虛擬貨幣</a>相關股票造好,CleanSpark升8.1%,Coinbase及Strategy升逾5%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">*美匯重上100關口*</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　美匯指數回穩,重上100整數關口,日內升0.79%,報100.661。美元兌<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日圓</a>出現反彈,升1.31%,報145.716。<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>兌美元維持近期震盪格局,交投於1.1300附近水平,日內跌0.64%,報1.12277。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　市場的避險情緒明顯降溫。<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>延續回調走勢,紐約期金跌2.49%,報每盎司3307.44美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　原油市場受美國和英國簽署貿易協議刺激,紐約期油升3.28%,報每桶59.98美元;布蘭特期油升2.96%,報每桶62.94美元。(jf)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
